cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CY 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning, specifically in the area of vector space models. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the impact of language on human judgments and machine predictions, which could fall under the categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves evaluation and correlation analysis, which could be relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper deals with multilingualism, which could be relevant to cs.CY (Computers and Society).
